description:
Alone in the Dark: Illumination (c)  Pure FPS

Release Date :  06/2015              Protection : Steam
Discs        :  1                    Genre      : Action

A darkness has fallen over the town of Lorwich. Monstrous hordes emerge
from beyond the realm of nightmares to sow chaos on the land. As one of
four heroes, you must battle the minions of the old ones with the force
of arms, and the power of illumination.


